pullRequest.body:
This PR provides a lemma `ShortComplex.SnakeInput.Î´_apply` which allows the computation of the connecting homomorphism in concrete categories. Incidentally, we also deduce from previous results that functors which preserve homology preserve finite limits and finite colimits.
